race.comment: VAREJAO (12) has been knocking on the door of a maiden victory placing in eight of ten overall and will be rock-hard fit for this fourth-up from the break. Can finally break the maiden status against this line-up. TARMAC (7) resumes here but the form he showed last preparation was good enough to be competitive in this contest. Can run a big race while fresh. DA SNOOP DOG (8) is facing the starter for the first time but has won both trials and any push in betting must be respected. INDAMOUSE (9) is another on debut but is sure to be well-educated from the Vandyke yard. Keep very safe. BOLD CHANGE (1) rounds out the selections with Wiggins on board.
